data.description: Discover tranquility at 13924 Amelia Drive in Kaplan, LA. This picturesque home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms across 1425 sqft, offering ample space for your family. A spacious covered carport welcomes you, ensuring convenience rain or shine. Additional storage is provided by a charming shed, perfect for stashing your outdoor gear. Situated in flood zone X, peace of mind accompanies every step. With eligibility for 100% financing, this residence is not just a dream--it's your reality awaiting fulfillment.
